:name:
Celeritas

:coretxt:
Vampire posses mystical inhuman speed. 
Can be used to impose penalty dice to opponent (when applicable), but only up to three.
Can also be used to act with super speed.

:cost:
1 Vigor per activation

:req:
Has raced against rising sun

:1:
Able to run at speed 50km/h. Add penalty die.

:2:
Able to run at speed 80km/h. Add two penalty dice.

:3:
Able to run at speed 130km/h. Add three penalty dice.

:tags:
Vampiric
VampiricStrength
